{
  "stem": "3988.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, just from day to day, that's-- you went, as I said before, you went to village and tried to-- tried to-- tried to-- to make a couple zlotys, you know, to feed us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they used to call me Schwarze [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tute. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tute ?] means a cat, and schwarze means black.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was little bit dark, so they called me Schwarze [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tuta. ?] My father used to call Schwarze [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Moshe, ?] because my father's name was [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Moshe ?] and he was dark to the color.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they called him Schwarze [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Moshe. ?] My mother, they called [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Chana ?] Bluma, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Chana ?] Bluma because she was a pretty girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that's how you know people, you know, by calling-- by-- by a nickname.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's how you did it in the old country, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one of them was limping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called him, you know, Moshe the [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Calaca ?] you know, or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One had a hunch back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they called him, you know, [INAUDIBLE], you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one had a-- a split lip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they called him Yankel with the [INAUDIBLE] on the lip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, that's how you know who you're talking about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- when the-- when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first day, the Germans walked in right at September-- September the 1st, 1939.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there approximately about 8 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we are not too far from the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the first thing, we went around there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and prior to that, where-- where we used to live, the street was the main street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could go to the German boarder.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
